  "instructions": [
    "Add olive oil to a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the katsuramuki-cut onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger, cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper, cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cottage cheese and Greek yogurt, cook, stirring constantly, until the cheese has melted and the mixture is smooth, about 5 minutes.",
    "Reduce heat to low, add the chopped parsley and chopped cilantro, stir to combine.",
    "Add the lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "Dot the top with unsalted butter and serve hot.",
    "Serve the Bouncy Rich Egyptian Cottage Cheese One-Pot hot, garnished with additional parsley and lemon wedges if desired."
